{"tid":1829276,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[堅持‧承諾] 不分和勇 抗爭融入生活 二百萬人日常活動","createTime":"2020-01-18T14:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T17:39:10.000Z","uid":27993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e2840865ff4e750a8b00b293c912d52ed3f9ea3f","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"首先，好重要！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&h=503c386d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭沒有降溫，不會停止。每個人都係自己崗位做現時做到既野。如果你覺得靜左，只係你靜左。唔好麻目，諗上自己可以做D咩，可唔可以做多D。<br />\n以下係香港最少想改變嗰200萬人都應該要做既野，而大部份人都冇上LIHKG，所以大家睇完幫手Share出去，俾所有和理非所有手足。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 黃色經濟圈 拒絕無良藍店 殺人紅店</span></span><br />\n <br />\n香港人支持黃色經濟圈時應已察覺，要一下子謝絕所有紅藍資本，好影響生活。<br />\n怕麻煩？已經有人擁抱更多麻煩，做左一系列既APP/ TG Channel，再整合做文宣方便你，請你Save左張圖，然後Add to favorite<br />\n堅持黃色經濟圈。生活習慣都改變唔到，談反抗？復仇？光復香港？<br />\n200萬人當中，一定有一班人因為麻煩，而忽視依樣野。既然不能一步到位，最少要循序漸進，先抵制藍紅大企業大集團，集中火力，逐一擊破<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">支持黃色經濟圈，最簡單由飲食開始。最少裝WhatsGap，和你Eat等等。一打開就有地圖，冇心機搵黃店至少唔好入藍店！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. $1和你交</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">除咗稅之外，但凡關於港共既繳款，水費grantloan，請堅持$1交。</span><br />\n攻略：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1811809/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1811809/page/1</a><br />\n當$1交錢出現既時間，港共有相應措施，限制每日交易次數，令$1交錢門檻上升。<br />\n記住，不論所有抗爭行為，對方一定有反制措施，依個時間要做既，唔係話依招冇用咁樣唔Work<br />\n而係要因應佢既反制措施再諗行動。<br />\n如果因為門檻高左而放棄，麻煩左而唔去做，咁樣每個抗爭行為都一定唔會有用。<br />\n因應佢既措施，我自己開多左3個銀行Account，冇IT背景上網自學Python，寫左4個Prog，每個銀行每日交$50，5日就可以交$1000，20個工作天可以交$4000 (仲有個別銀行係冇限制架)<br />\n如是者我每個月既電子月結單係80頁既$1<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">面對極權阻撓，我地要做既係堅持，反抗，絕對唔係放棄！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. Twitter Reddit 聯署 國際戰線</span></span><br />\nTwitter TG Bot: <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=d927077b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n聯署Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=6ee1c23d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HDZuKhbHPjQnjA0S2bsaKg</a><br />\n聯署機攻略: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1827349/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1827349/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 聯署係最容易，小朋友都做到既野，<span style=\"color: red;\">每日抽少少時間，禁兩個掣。</span><br />\n同樣地，有手足已經將好麻煩既野自己做曬，為既係令大家可以更方便，希望大家可以一齊堅持落去。<br />\n聯署Channel只要有10萬人，而入左去既人每次都簽名，基本上聯署一出，就可以夠人。當然10萬係唔夠，愈多愈好。<br />\n<br />\n比較難做既係，支共已經有大量網軍係唔同平台抹黑香港人<br />\n大家可以係Reddit Twitter幫手解話反抹黑，俾更多外國人知道真相。<br />\n如果失敗，共產黨最後一步係抹殺香港人，共產黨一定會咁做。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 文宣 日程 快閃連儂開花</span></span><br />\n快閃連儂開花: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1819022/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1819022/page/1</a><br />\n文宣集合TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=80d4e405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n每個地方都係連儂牆，有攻略有教學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要快推日程！</span><br />\n平時可以幫手Share多D文宣 日程 Airdrop又好 諗到既都去做<br />\n要知道依加班狗追住文宣組，連儂手咬，亦有好多人被票控<br />\n唔好再期待其他人去幫你做你應該做既野啦<br />\n<br />\n煲底見！"},{"pid":"5e1199802843e208c61e8904578105c3450c546f","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span>"},{"pid":"bf09abc484d5ec26cebee721d874fbfd388c95bc","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f64aaa00184a3cfd645f255202b78cf8b045b219","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span>"},{"pid":"f98ce1b64ab45338e05efe28a4236e3d47ebef49","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"5cd9d1446bd16eb81ff395eb2557c1488bc44110","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" />"},{"pid":"e9031c60bee6aee50da44b3d939e5b1e39e0726a","tid":1829276,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T17:33:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/1LFOYAB.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lih.kg%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LFOYAB.gif&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1CWHaP8IcnP8